abstract: >-
  Reproducible pipeline and manuscript demonstrating empirical 
  long-range dependence / fractal memory across multiple domains
  (Bitcoin/crypto volatility, earthquake activity, physiology/HRV, 
  genomics) using DFA-2, bootstrap confidence intervals, and 
  phase-randomized surrogate tests. This package extends LRD v5 
  (Monte-Carlo validation on synthetic fGn) with real-world 
  empirical evidence.
